    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul and subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with crisp turn-in, and the throttle response remains sharp thanks to the individual throttle bodies. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and track-ready.",
