    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor, localized imperfections like small stone chips on the hood that are typical of regular road use. Inside, the cabin is impeccably clean and free of odors; the upholstery is supple with no tears, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every feature, including the power-adjustable seats, infotainment system, and ice-cold air conditioning, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a documented history of on-time oil changes and fluid flushes. The brakes are responsive, and the tires have significant tread remaining. This car has been garage-kept and treated with respect, offering the next owner a turn-key experience with no immediate maintenance required.",
